                                                       Project Kronos User Story

As a user I’d like to be able to login . 
Once in the job, I’d like to start recording my time as well as my location. 
I’d like to be able to have a way to record tasks accomplish.
I’d like to be able to see all my current/ still open 
Make invoice for customer.
Possibly have a way to record a picture. 
I’d like to have a way to record milage. 
I’d like to be able to have a way to move from one job to the next.
Task or customer specific. 


